name: Config 2022 Name Card - Tshering Yudon
description: I've been freelancing for the past year and working on my own without being part of a team, so I am looking forward to meeting design friends from all over the world. I'm currently relearning Japanese and learning Spanish, so maybe we could also become language partners. Find me on LinkedIn! Reading the 10 arguments for leaving social media by Jaron Lanier, so currently not using social media accounts.
